John P. Jones III

Age : 65Public asset : 4,500,351 USDLinked companies :  Automatic Data Processing 





Summary 



Mr. John P. Jones, III, is Non-Executive Chairman at Automatic Data Processing, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at American Chemistry Council, Inc. Mr. Jones was previously employed as an Independent Director by Sunoco, Inc., President by Air Products Europe, Inc., and Chairman by Air Products & Chemicals, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Villanova University.



